description: It has been 27 days since the last recorded transmission of the virus on the island.
title: Coronavirus: Guernsey has no 'known' cases
title_page: Coronavirus: Guernsey has no 'known' cases - BBC News
maintext: Director of public health Dr Nicola Brink said the move to no known active cases was a "testament to how well the community have worked with us", but cautioned against complacency.
